The Three Vibes: Your Inner Compass
Every card in Starlight Deck carries one of three vibes. These aren't just categories — they're
energetic signatures that reflect different aspects of your journey.
■ Acuity — The Lens of Clarity
Color: Deep cosmic blue (#59a6ff)
Element: Air / Mind
Keywords: Insight, precision, focus, truth, discernment
Acuity cards call you to see clearly. They cut through fog, reveal patterns, and ask you to examine
what's really there. When Acuity appears often, your journey needs mental clarity and honest
assessment.
■ Valor — The Fire of Action
Color: Bold crimson red (#ff5b5b)
Element: Fire / Will
Keywords: Courage, momentum, risk, boldness, vitality
Valor cards ignite the warrior spirit. They encourage leaps, brave choices, and forward movement
even when the path is unclear. Drawing heavy Valor suggests it's time to act, not just think.
■ Variety — The Dance of Possibility
Color: Warm golden amber (#ffe27a)
Element: Earth / Flux
Keywords: Adaptability, exploration, playfulness, change, abundance
Variety cards remind you that life is multifaceted. They speak to flexibility, trying new approaches,
and not getting too rigid. A Variety-heavy draw suggests you may need to explore options rather than
commit to one path.
Careons (■) — The Currency of Care
The name Careon comes from 'care on' — a reminder that this currency represents attention,
intention, and community support. It's not about hoarding wealth; it's about circulating energy.
