Community Features — Connection Beyond Cards
SLD Network Fund
The Starlight Deck Network Fund is a shared pool that grows through collective play. When it
reaches milestones (like 1,000 ■), the community unlocks rewards together. This isn't competitive —
there's no leaderboard. Everyone wins when the fund grows.
Community Phrases (The Ticker)
For 100 ■, anyone can submit a phrase (max 20 characters) that appears in the scrolling ticker at the
top of the experience. This isn't advertising — it's collective expression. The phrases become a
living record of the community's thoughts, hopes, and humor.
Examples of great phrases:
• 'Trust the process ■'
• 'QUANTUM: Still here, still growing'
• 'Zeniths are gifts, not goals'
